msgid "This errand needs you."
msgstr ""

#: .\Modification_Files\NPC\v_npc_mission.json
msgid ""
"Blood... Our main food for darkest centuries. Even I almost forgot its "
"taste, I'd like to drink it again. Bring me 30, too much but it is essential"
" in many ways."
