"Gather <color_light_red>15 small leech teeth</color> and give them to the "
"commando. They are rarely dropped by <color_magenta>leeches</color> that "
"lives in the <color_light_blue>swamp</color>."
msgstr ""

#: .\Modification_Files\NPC\v_npc_mission.json
msgid "I want you to slay something..."
msgstr ""

#: .\Modification_Files\NPC\v_npc_mission.json
msgid ""
"Ofcourse you know about the bloodsucking pests on the swamp, we hate those "
"parasites squirming for blood to live. Hand over 15 of their teeth as a "
"proof to succeed this trial."
msgstr ""

#: .\Modification_Files\NPC\v_npc_mission.json
msgid "Slay them in any way you want."
msgstr ""

#: .\Modification_Files\NPC\v_npc_mission.json
msgid "It's just okay."
msgstr ""

#: .\Modification_Files\NPC\v_npc_mission.json
msgid "They are blind, and depends on what they hear or smell."
msgstr ""

#: .\Modification_Files\NPC\v_npc_mission.json
msgid "Got 'em?"
msgstr ""

#: .\Modification_Files\NPC\v_npc_mission.json
msgid "Nice work, I guess they won't bother us for a long time."
msgstr ""

#: .\Modification_Files\NPC\v_npc_mission.json
msgid "*slurping*"
