"completion.  <color_magenta>Elder zombies</color> are depicted to their "
"stone-like, compact blood and are rarely seen in the "
"<color_light_blue>graveyards</color>."
msgstr ""

#: .\Modification_Files\NPC\v_npc_mission.json
msgid "This is a little harder..."
msgstr ""

#: .\Modification_Files\NPC\v_npc_mission.json
msgid ""
"The gravestone in this crypt were built long ago, and the dead bodies has "
"been buried here since before I reside here. Surprisingly, they were "
"resurrected with this odd \"magic\". I want you to take 10 of them down and "
"let their hollow vessel for an eternal rest."
msgstr ""

#: .\Modification_Files\NPC\v_npc_mission.json
msgid "Good. Now go outside and look for them."
msgstr ""

#: .\Modification_Files\NPC\v_npc_mission.json
msgid "Come back later."
msgstr ""

#: .\Modification_Files\NPC\v_npc_mission.json
msgid ""
"Their blood has calcified into a shell, and it is distinctive to their "
"appearance."
msgstr ""

#: .\Modification_Files\NPC\v_npc_mission.json
msgid "Now?"
msgstr ""

#: .\Modification_Files\NPC\v_npc_mission.json
msgid "I know you can do it..."
msgstr ""

#: .\Modification_Files\NPC\v_npc_mission.json
msgid "*glares*"
msgstr ""

#: .\Modification_Files\NPC\v_npc_mission.json
msgid "Bring a bloodrune"
msgstr ""

#. ~ Description for mission '{'str': 'Bring a bloodrune'}'
#: .\Modification_Files\NPC\v_npc_mission.json
msgid ""
"Get a <color_light_red>bloodrune</color> then deliver it to the vampire."
msgstr ""

#: .\Modification_Files\NPC\v_npc_mission.json
msgid "This is a bit hard for you. You still want to try?"
msgstr ""

#: .\Modification_Files\NPC\v_npc_mission.json
msgid ""
"Bloodrune... The vampire's eternal soul. Merely a fact that few of us night creatures turn into an object upon death, yet most resists to that point.\n"
"In the dark days, bloodrunes are set in a pedestal by elder civilizations, and said that their \"god\" will accept it as a praise, which is not true. Get this rune for me, to honor its soul in a way we normally do."
msgstr ""

#: .\Modification_Files\NPC\v_npc_mission.json
msgid "Good."
msgstr ""

#: .\Modification_Files\NPC\v_npc_mission.json
msgid "Just do it later on."
msgstr ""

#: .\Modification_Files\NPC\v_npc_mission.json
msgid ""
"A vampire's death is a big success to those elderly jerks. Well, it is their"
" belief that can't be bothered in any way."
msgstr ""

#: .\Modification_Files\NPC\v_npc_mission.json
msgid "Got it?"
msgstr ""

#: .\Modification_Files\NPC\v_npc_mission.json
msgid ""
"I thank you for this rune.\n"
"*Shatters it by hand*\n"
msgstr ""

#: .\Modification_Files\NPC\v_npc_mission.json
msgid "Just thanks..."
msgstr ""

#: .\Modification_Files\NPC\v_npc_mission.json
msgid "*smirks*"
msgstr ""

#: .\Modification_Files\NPC\v_npc_mission.json
msgid "Take Vampire to the Cove"
msgstr ""

#. ~ Description for mission '{'str': 'Take Vampire to the Cove'}'
#: .\Modification_Files\NPC\v_npc_mission.json
msgid "Escort the vampire to the <color_light_blue>vampire cove</color>."
msgstr ""

#: .\Modification_Files\NPC\v_npc_mission.json
msgid "This is the last job, you want to do it?"
msgstr ""

#: .\Modification_Files\NPC\v_npc_mission.json
msgid ""
"Since you've been helping me for a while, I will need you to travel with me "
"to the vampire cove. Being isolated for centuries is a great experience, but"
" seeing a living community of my kind alleviates my frozen body the most."
msgstr ""

#: .\Modification_Files\NPC\v_npc_mission.json
msgid ""
"Good, those tests proved yourself a good descendant. As a reward, I'll "
"protect you along the way."
msgstr ""

#: .\Modification_Files\NPC\v_npc_mission.json
msgid "Just okay, get back later..."
msgstr ""

#: .\Modification_Files\NPC\v_npc_mission.json
msgid ""
"This may be a long journey. You know I'm a night creature, so you'll have to"
" take care of me in daytime."
msgstr ""

#: .\Modification_Files\NPC\v_npc_mission.json
msgid "What?"
msgstr ""

#: .\Modification_Files\NPC\v_npc_mission.json
msgid ""
"I see my kindred seems alright. Well, it does matter to me, and you've been "
"the key to this. Thank you, descendant."
msgstr ""

#: .\Modification_Files\NPC\v_npc_mission.json
msgid "Get 2 Corrupt Bloodrune Stone"
msgstr ""

#. ~ Description for mission '{'str': 'Get 2 Corrupt Bloodrune Stone'}'
#: .\Modification_Files\NPC\v_npc_mission.json
msgid ""
"Get the <color_light_red>2 corrupted bloodrune stones</color> that are "
"dropped by killing the <color_magenta>infected vampires</color> then deliver"
" them to the trader."
msgstr ""

#: .\Modification_Files\NPC\v_npc_mission.json
msgid "Well, actually we have a problem..."
msgstr ""

#: .\Modification_Files\NPC\v_npc_mission.json
msgid ""
"Our kin isn't a target of diseases, but those 2 vampires at the back, they "
"really look bad and start raging on its own, so we cage them at early "
"state... Never knew the magic was that strong enough to kill EVEN us. I want"
" you to end the sick vampires as your task and get their corrupted "
"bloodrune. We know we can dispose them easily, but our beliefs prevent us "
"from killing our own kind."
msgstr ""

#: .\Modification_Files\NPC\v_npc_mission.json
msgid "Thank you, now go."
msgstr ""

#: .\Modification_Files\NPC\v_npc_mission.json
msgid "You need to do that later."
msgstr ""

#: .\Modification_Files\NPC\v_npc_mission.json
msgid "Serious pain you'll get from breaking into their cage."
msgstr ""

#: .\Modification_Files\NPC\v_npc_mission.json
msgid "What happened there?"
msgstr ""

#: .\Modification_Files\NPC\v_npc_mission.json
msgid ""
"Great, mortal. This oozing bloodrune will now meet its place... Or not at "
"all."
msgstr ""

#: .\Modification_Files\NPC\v_npc_mission.json
msgid "*glaressharply*"
msgstr ""

#: .\Modification_Files\NPC\v_npc_mission.json
msgid "Slay 10 bats"
msgstr ""

#. ~ Description for mission '{'str': 'Slay 10 bats'}'
#: .\Modification_Files\NPC\v_npc_mission.json
msgid ""
"Kill <color_magenta>10 bats</color> then talk to the trader after "
"completion. <color_magenta>Bats</color> are commonly seen at "
"<color_gray>nighttime</color> or inside a <color_light_blue>cave</color>."
msgstr ""

#: .\Modification_Files\NPC\v_npc_mission.json
msgid "We do appreciate your assistance with our needs."
msgstr ""

#: .\Modification_Files\NPC\v_npc_mission.json
msgid ""
"Vampire bats became literal bloodsuckers these passing days and I want you "
"to hunt down 10 of these vermins. We've been swarmed by these creatures "
"lately but gladly we managed to shove them away."
msgstr ""

#: .\Modification_Files\NPC\v_npc_mission.json
msgid "Good. Come back anytime you want."
msgstr ""

#: .\Modification_Files\NPC\v_npc_mission.json
msgid "I guess you're afraid of bats..."
msgstr ""

#: .\Modification_Files\NPC\v_npc_mission.json
msgid "Bats are nocturnal, and tends to live in dark places like caves."
msgstr ""

#: .\Modification_Files\NPC\v_npc_mission.json
msgid "Thank you for your help in eradicating some bloodsuckers."
msgstr ""

#: .\Modification_Files\NPC\v_npc_mission.json
msgid "Go to a forgotten burial site"
msgstr ""

#. ~ Description for mission '{'str': 'Go to a forgotten burial site'}'
#: .\Modification_Files\NPC\v_npc_mission.json
msgid ""
" Travel to a <color_light_blue>burial site</color> then talk to the seeker."
msgstr ""

#: .\Modification_Files\NPC\v_npc_mission.json
msgid "Before we go, the trader asked me a request on this journey."
msgstr ""

#: .\Modification_Files\NPC\v_npc_mission.json
msgid ""
"The trader told me to observe the old graveyards we knew from the past. So "
"before we go to the outskirts, we'll get pass through it first."
msgstr ""

#: .\Modification_Files\NPC\v_npc_mission.json
msgid "Off we go, mortal."
msgstr ""

#: .\Modification_Files\NPC\v_npc_mission.json
msgid "Well, that's your choice..."
msgstr ""

#: .\Modification_Files\NPC\v_npc_mission.json
msgid "Its been a long time since I see those graves..."
msgstr ""

#: .\Modification_Files\NPC\v_npc_mission.json
msgid "What now?"
msgstr ""

#: .\Modification_Files\NPC\v_npc_mission.json
msgid ""
"The magic took over the buried corpses? That's unfortunate and the trader "
"would be disappointed about this..."
msgstr ""

#: .\Modification_Files\NPC\v_npc_mission.json
msgid "Go to the wasteland outskirts"
msgstr ""

#. ~ Description for mission '{'str': 'Go to the wasteland outskirts'}'
#: .\Modification_Files\NPC\v_npc_mission.json
msgid ""
"Along with the seeker, travel to the <color_light_blue>wasteland "
"outskirts</color>. Talk to them again after reaching the destination."
msgstr ""

#: .\Modification_Files\NPC\v_npc_mission.json
msgid "Are we ready for this trip?"
msgstr ""

#: .\Modification_Files\NPC\v_npc_mission.json
msgid ""
"We are now going to the outskirts, and I know the commando told you about "
"this place."
msgstr ""

#: .\Modification_Files\NPC\v_npc_mission.json
msgid "Good. Now off we go, mortal."
msgstr ""

#: .\Modification_Files\NPC\v_npc_mission.json
#: .\Modification_Files\NPC\v_npc_responds\Underrefugee\v_ug_responses.json
#: .\Modification_Files\NPC\v_npc_responds\Underrefugee\v_us_responses.json
#: .\Modification_Files\NPC\v_npc_responds\Underrefugee\v_ut_responses.json
msgid "..."
msgstr ""

#: .\Modification_Files\NPC\v_npc_mission.json
msgid ""
"I'll give you some details about the outskirts. It is a large structure with"
" barricaded walls and tents placed outside for human survivors. It also has "
"a barn and farm fields that provides descent food, and shopkeepers sell "
"various stuff there."
msgstr ""

#: .\Modification_Files\NPC\v_npc_mission.json
msgid ""
"\"What else could I do for you\" you say? Don't worry, I have no more "
"requests for you. Ask anyone here if you're curious. When you're done, talk "
"to me."
msgstr ""

#: .\Modification_Files\NPC\v_npc_mission.json
msgid "Ummm...."
msgstr ""

#: .\Modification_Files\NPC\v_npc_mission.json
msgid "Recruit Radio Specialist"
msgstr ""

#. ~ Description for mission '{'str': 'Recruit Radio Specialist'}'
#: .\Modification_Files\NPC\v_npc_mission.json
msgid ""
"Ask the <color_yellow>Radio Specialist</color> to join, then talk to the "
"guard after they did."
msgstr ""

#: .\Modification_Files\NPC\v_npc_mission.json
msgid "It's easy, I think..."
msgstr ""

#: .\Modification_Files\NPC\v_npc_mission.json
msgid ""
"First things first, we have to build a radio tower that transmit signals to "
"our fellow survivors out in the wilds which serves as their waypoint to our "
"place. Well, building that cheap structure is simple, but what I want you to"
" do is to find a person with expertise to operate this kind of stuff."
msgstr ""

#: .\Modification_Files\NPC\v_npc_mission.json
msgid "Great. Now move, mortal."
msgstr ""

#: .\Modification_Files\NPC\v_npc_mission.json
msgid "Great! Let this survivors die out of nowhere then..."
msgstr ""

#: .\Modification_Files\NPC\v_npc_mission.json
msgid "Just bring them in safely."
msgstr ""

#: .\Modification_Files\NPC\v_npc_mission.json
msgid "Where are they?"
msgstr ""

#: .\Modification_Files\NPC\v_npc_mission.json
msgid "I knew you can bring one. Now let this nerd go to work!"
msgstr ""

#: .\Modification_Files\NPC\v_npc_mission.json
msgid "Slay the succumbed vampire"
msgstr ""

#. ~ Description for mission '{'str': 'Slay the succumbed vampire'}'
#: .\Modification_Files\NPC\v_npc_mission.json
msgid ""
"Kill the <color_magenta>succumbed vampire</color> then talk to the guard.\n"
"<color_red>Going unprepared is a death trap!</color>"
msgstr ""

#: .\Modification_Files\NPC\v_npc_mission.json
msgid ""
"With the radio working well, we will be able to connect to the outsiders and"
" hope for them to receive our message. Yet there's this vampire I am worried"
" about, wandering the cursed lands and wicked to its vile nature. Our "
"scouting patrol knows the coordinates, and I want you to put it down "
"immediately before it brings wrath to other survivors."
msgstr ""

#: .\Modification_Files\NPC\v_npc_mission.json
msgid ""
"With it wielding the power of an immortal, provoking unprepared is a "
"suicidal act."
msgstr ""

#: .\Modification_Files\NPC\v_npc_mission.json
msgid "The monster does not rest after a kill..."
msgstr ""

#: .\Modification_Files\NPC\v_npc_mission.json
msgid ""
"Bring guns and keep your distance, us vampires will take down humans for "
"almost instantly."
msgstr ""

#: .\Modification_Files\NPC\v_npc_mission.json
msgid "Is it dead?"
msgstr ""

#: .\Modification_Files\NPC\v_npc_mission.json
msgid "Fascinating job mortal! With its death, others will be safe... A bit."
msgstr ""

#: .\Modification_Files\NPC\v_npc_mission.json
msgid "Destroy the vampirus"
msgstr ""

#. ~ Description for mission '{'str': 'Destroy the vampirus'}'
#: .\Modification_Files\NPC\v_npc_mission.json
msgid ""
"With the help of the <color_yellow>seeker</color>, locate and destroy the <color_light_blue>vampirus</color>, the place where <color_magenta>infected vampires</color> gather.\n"
"<color_red>Going unprepared is a death trap!</color>"
msgstr ""

#: .\Modification_Files\NPC\v_npc_mission.json
msgid ""
"Unfortunately, that vampire is not alone.\n"
"\n"
"I have recently received a radio message that reveals the pinpoint location of the gathering place owned by those infected vampires. Your task is to find a way to stop and annihilate the entire army of them. I told the seeker about it and she'll help you infiltrate your objective."
msgstr ""

#: .\Modification_Files\NPC\v_npc_mission.json
msgid ""
"Good. Just remind her about it and she'll provide the essential information."
msgstr ""

#: .\Modification_Files\NPC\v_npc_mission.json
msgid "Alright then, let's talk about it again later..."
msgstr ""

#: .\Modification_Files\NPC\v_npc_mission.json
msgid "Be aware. If alone is dangerous, more so when they're dozen."
msgstr ""

#: .\Modification_Files\NPC\v_npc_mission.json
msgid "Report?"
msgstr ""

#: .\Modification_Files\NPC\v_npc_mission.json
msgid ""
"Unbelievable! You did it, mortal! Our master would be grateful of your "
"doings!"
msgstr ""

#: .\Modification_Files\NPC\v_npc_mission.json
msgid "Travel to the vampirus"
msgstr ""

#. ~ Description for mission '{'str': 'Travel to the vampirus'}'
#: .\Modification_Files\NPC\v_npc_mission.json
msgid ""
"Along with the seeker, travel to the <color_light_blue>vampirus</color>."
msgstr ""

#: .\Modification_Files\NPC\v_npc_mission.json
msgid "Lead the trail, I'm right behind if you require my assistance."
msgstr ""

#: .\Modification_Files\NPC\v_npc_mission.json
msgid "Keep an eye out for possible threats along the way."
msgstr ""

#: .\Modification_Files\NPC\v_npc_mission.json
msgid "Are we in our destination?"
msgstr ""

#: .\Modification_Files\NPC\v_npc_mission.json
msgid ""
"Now that we're here, we have to locate the entrance that leads to the "
"depths."
msgstr ""

#: .\Modification_Files\NPC\v_npc_mission.json
msgid "Unseal the entrance"
msgstr ""

#. ~ Description for mission '{'str': 'Unseal the entrance'}'
#: .\Modification_Files\NPC\v_npc_mission.json
msgid ""
"Protect the seeker from the <color_magenta>zeds</color> attracted to your "
"location."
msgstr ""

#: .\Modification_Files\NPC\v_npc_mission.json
msgid "Yes, I can unseal it at this point."
msgstr ""

#: .\Modification_Files\NPC\v_npc_mission.json
msgid ""
"I do not guarantee our safety from breaking the seal, so you'll need to "
"guard me as I break it."
msgstr ""

#: .\Modification_Files\NPC\v_npc_mission.json
msgid ""
"With the smell of blood coming out of the vampirus, zombies are attracted "
"towards our location."
msgstr ""

#: .\Modification_Files\NPC\v_npc_mission.json
msgid "And now that the seal is broken, we can go through it."
msgstr ""

#: .\Modification_Files\NPC\v_npc_mission.json
msgid "Bring Radio Specialist to the outskirts"
msgstr ""

#. ~ Description for mission '{'str': 'Bring Radio Specialist to the
#. outskirts'}'
#: .\Modification_Files\NPC\v_npc_mission.json
msgid ""
"Escort the specialist to the <color_light_blue>wasteland outskirts</color>."
msgstr ""

#: .\Modification_Files\NPC\v_npc_mission.json
msgid "We're going, right?"
msgstr ""

#: .\Modification_Files\NPC\v_npc_mission.json
msgid "We have to go to that place and I need you to lead the way."
msgstr ""

#: .\Modification_Files\NPC\v_npc_mission.json
msgid "Just remember to keep everything fine as we go there."
msgstr ""

#: .\Modification_Files\NPC\v_npc_mission.json
msgid "Well, your words are useless..."
msgstr ""

#: .\Modification_Files\NPC\v_npc_mission.json
msgid "From what direction did you came from? I suppose that's the right way."
msgstr ""

#: .\Modification_Files\NPC\v_npc_mission.json
msgid ""
"This place looks neat! Now that I'm here, I'll do my job as you have said "
"earlier."
msgstr ""

#: .\Modification_Files\NPC\v_npc_mission.json
msgid "Bring Prisoner to the outskirts"
msgstr ""

#. ~ Description for mission '{'str': 'Bring Prisoner to the outskirts'}'
#: .\Modification_Files\NPC\v_npc_mission.json
msgid ""
"Take the prisoner to the <color_light_blue>wasteland outskirts</color>."
msgstr ""

#: .\Modification_Files\NPC\v_npc_mission.json
msgid "Lead me to that place, then..."
msgstr ""

#: .\Modification_Files\NPC\v_npc_mission.json
msgid "Awesome!"
msgstr ""

#: .\Modification_Files\NPC\v_npc_mission.json
msgid "Well, atleast you've made me happy before my fate..."
msgstr ""

#: .\Modification_Files\NPC\v_npc_mission.json
msgid ""
"You need my advice for this? I could say something if I'm already free in "
"the wilderness..."
msgstr ""

#: .\Modification_Files\NPC\v_npc_mission.json
msgid ""
"Damn! This place is like a fortress! But you should've warned me about the "
"vampires living here... They freak me out everytime I see one..."
msgstr ""

#: .\Modification_Files\NPC\v_npc_mission.json
msgid "Reach a memorial crypt"
msgstr ""

#. ~ Description for mission '{'str': 'Reach a memorial crypt'}'
#: .\Modification_Files\NPC\v_npc_mission.json
msgid ""
"Travel to a <color_light_blue>memorial crypt</color> then inspect its "
"surroundings."
msgstr ""

#: .\Modification_Files\NPC\v_npc_mission.json
msgid "Dark Descendant"
msgstr ""

#. ~ Description for mission '{'str': 'Dark Descendant'}'
#: .\Modification_Files\NPC\v_npc_mission.json
msgid ""
"Ask a <color_yellow>lone vampire</color> to join your party.\n"
"You must earn their trust by doing their favor."
msgstr ""

#: .\Modification_Files\NPC\v_npc_mission_items.json
msgid "corrupted bloodrune stone"
msgid_plural "corrupted bloodrune stones"
msgstr[0] ""
msgstr[1] ""

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'corrupted bloodrune stone'}
#: .\Modification_Files\NPC\v_npc_mission_items.json
msgid ""
"A black, gooey bloodrune stone specifically owned by an infected vampire. It"
" no longer pulsate and the markings are completely erased."
msgstr ""

#: .\Modification_Files\NPC\v_npc_mission_items.json
msgid "small leech tooth"
msgid_plural "small leech teeth"
msgstr[0] ""
msgstr[1] ""

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'small leech tooth', 'str_pl': 'small leech
#. teeth'}
#: .\Modification_Files\NPC\v_npc_mission_items.json
msgid ""
"A tooth size of the human fingernails. It is sharp, but too small to be used"
" as a tool."
msgstr ""

#: .\Modification_Files\NPC\v_npc_mission_items.json
msgid "blood sac"
msgid_plural "blood sacs"
msgstr[0] ""
msgstr[1] ""

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'blood sac'}
#: .\Modification_Files\NPC\v_npc_mission_items.json
msgid "The large sac of the devourer leech."
msgstr ""

#: .\Modification_Files\NPC\Backgrounds\lonevamp_s1.json
msgid ""
"It was my time to hunt down a prey. Moon's in its peak, everything's "
"peaceful... But all crumbles so quickly that night, after sighting this "
"woman at the forest trail, weeping, tending to her grievous wound."
msgstr ""

#: .\Modification_Files\NPC\Backgrounds\lonevamp_s1.json
msgid "What about her?."
msgstr ""

#: .\Modification_Files\NPC\Backgrounds\lonevamp_s1.json
msgid "Her wound?"
msgstr ""

#: .\Modification_Files\NPC\Backgrounds\lonevamp_s1.json
msgid "<done_conversation_section>"
msgstr ""

#: .\Modification_Files\NPC\Backgrounds\lonevamp_s1.json
msgid "<end_talking>"
msgstr ""

#: .\Modification_Files\NPC\Backgrounds\lonevamp_s1.json
msgid ""
"From my observation, she's at her mid-life, fully dressed with her bag full "
"of supplies."
msgstr ""

#: .\Modification_Files\NPC\Backgrounds\lonevamp_s1.json
msgid "What about her wound?"
msgstr ""

#: .\Modification_Files\NPC\Backgrounds\lonevamp_s1.json
msgid ""
"I did not come closer, but I took a deeper look. From what I have seen, "
"there's this gooey black substance, pumping slowly into her."
msgstr ""

#: .\Modification_Files\NPC\Backgrounds\lonevamp_s1.json
msgid "Do you have any idea what it is?"
msgstr ""

#: .\Modification_Files\NPC\Backgrounds\lonevamp_s1.json
msgid "No. But in my belief, its a parasite that sucks life from its host."
msgstr ""

#: .\Modification_Files\NPC\Backgrounds\lonevamp_s1.json
msgid "So, what did you do after that?"
msgstr ""

#: .\Modification_Files\NPC\Backgrounds\lonevamp_s1.json
msgid ""
"I stalked her through the trail. My curiosity kept my thirst aside for some "
"moment, 'till she suddenly spasms to the ground. I approach her and inspect "
"his vitality, finding out she's dead. Her veins turn black and her eyes "
"oozing with goo. I tried to close her eyelids, but then she immediately bit "
"my <swear> hand!"
msgstr ""

#: .\Modification_Files\NPC\Backgrounds\lonevamp_s1.json
msgid "Woah, that is horrifying!"
msgstr ""

#: .\Modification_Files\NPC\Backgrounds\lonevamp_s1.json
msgid ""
"In quick response, I slam her <swear> head against the ground and explodes into a mass of gore!\n"
"Well, fortunately her bite isn't that deep, but I swear I'll <swear> break their skulls before I get too close to them again!"
msgstr ""

#: .\Modification_Files\NPC\Backgrounds\v_background_list.json
msgid "<BGSS_intro_question>"
msgstr ""

#: .\Modification_Files\NPC\v_npc_responds\Isolated\v_lo_responses.json
#: .\Modification_Files\NPC\v_npc_responds\Underrefugee\v_uc_responses.json
msgid "Here's your blood."
msgstr ""

#: .\Modification_Files\NPC\v_npc_responds\Isolated\v_lo_responses.json
msgid "Here's your bloodrune stone."
msgstr ""

#: .\Modification_Files\NPC\v_npc_responds\Isolated\v_lo_responses.json
msgid "Greetings, human."
msgstr ""

#: .\Modification_Files\NPC\v_npc_responds\Isolated\v_lo_responses.json
#: .\Modification_Files\NPC\v_npc_responds\Wastelands_Outskirts\v_wg1_responses.json
msgid "What is it, mortal?"
msgstr ""

#: .\Modification_Files\NPC\v_npc_responds\Isolated\v_lo_responses.json
msgid "Speak up, mortal."
msgstr ""

#: .\Modification_Files\NPC\v_npc_responds\Isolated\v_lo_responses.json
#: .\Modification_Files\NPC\v_npc_responds\Underrefugee\v_ug_responses.json
msgid "Tell me about yourself."
msgstr ""

#: .\Modification_Files\NPC\v_npc_responds\Isolated\v_lo_responses.json
msgid "Why are you here?"
msgstr ""

#: .\Modification_Files\NPC\v_npc_responds\Isolated\v_lo_responses.json
msgid "Greetings, my brethren."
msgstr ""

#: .\Modification_Files\NPC\v_npc_responds\Isolated\v_lo_responses.json
msgid "About that quest..."
msgstr ""

#: .\Modification_Files\NPC\v_npc_responds\Isolated\v_lo_responses.json
msgid "Ummm... You want to stick with me?"
msgstr ""

#: .\Modification_Files\NPC\v_npc_responds\Isolated\v_lo_responses.json
msgid "I'm vacant for your needs."
msgstr ""

#: .\Modification_Files\NPC\v_npc_responds\Isolated\v_lo_responses.json
msgid "Sorry to bother."
msgstr ""

#: .\Modification_Files\NPC\v_npc_responds\Isolated\v_lo_responses.json
msgid ""
"I am a vampire, preserved for centuries. But you see, I enshroud myself in "
"the shadows of the past."
msgstr ""

#: .\Modification_Files\NPC\v_npc_responds\Isolated\v_lo_responses.json
msgid "Preserved?"
msgstr ""

#: .\Modification_Files\NPC\v_npc_responds\Isolated\v_lo_responses.json
#: .\Modification_Files\NPC\v_npc_responds\Underrefugee\v_uc_responses.json
#: .\Modification_Files\NPC\v_npc_responds\Underrefugee\v_us_responses.json
#: .\Modification_Files\NPC\v_npc_responds\Vampirus\h_prison_cell.json
#: .\Modification_Files\NPC\v_npc_responds\Wastelands_Outskirts\h_wrs_responses.json
#: .\Modification_Files\NPC\v_npc_responds\Wastelands_Outskirts\v_wg2_responses.json
msgid "Okay."
msgstr ""

#: .\Modification_Files\NPC\v_npc_responds\Isolated\v_lo_responses.json
msgid ""
"I live here as my peaceful sanctuary for a very long time. Though the world "
"is in chaos, I am not bothered nor assaulted by those things."
msgstr ""

#: .\Modification_Files\NPC\v_npc_responds\Isolated\v_lo_responses.json
msgid "Is there a some sort of place like this?"
msgstr ""

#: .\Modification_Files\NPC\v_npc_responds\Isolated\v_lo_responses.json
#: .\Modification_Files\NPC\v_npc_responds\Underrefugee\v_ug_responses.json
#: .\Modification_Files\NPC\v_npc_responds\Underrefugee\v_us_responses.json
#: .\Modification_Files\NPC\v_npc_responds\Wastelands_Outskirts\v_wg1_responses.json
msgid "Okay then..."
msgstr ""

#: .\Modification_Files\NPC\v_npc_responds\Isolated\v_lo_responses.json
msgid ""
"That marking... I see you've been helping my kindred with their troubles."
msgstr ""

#: .\Modification_Files\NPC\v_npc_responds\Isolated\v_lo_responses.json
msgid "Just like others, you want me as a slave... I refuse, mortal."
msgstr ""

#: .\Modification_Files\NPC\v_npc_responds\Isolated\v_lo_responses.json
msgid "I just want you as an odd friend... I'm sorry."
msgstr ""

#: .\Modification_Files\NPC\v_npc_responds\Isolated\v_lo_responses.json
msgid "I want you to go on a journey with me."
msgstr ""

#: .\Modification_Files\NPC\v_npc_responds\Isolated\v_lo_responses.json
msgid "No, I want you to go on a journey with me."
msgstr ""

#: .\Modification_Files\NPC\v_npc_responds\Isolated\v_lo_responses.json
msgid ""
"It is the prowess that all immortals have, and we tend to refine this by "
"concealing ourselves from humanity."
msgstr ""

#: .\Modification_Files\NPC\v_npc_responds\Isolated\v_lo_responses.json
msgid "Too bad."
msgstr ""

#: .\Modification_Files\NPC\v_npc_responds\Isolated\v_lo_responses.json
msgid ""
"Yes it is. Its a small community of night creatures tending to theirselves "
"to live in peace."
msgstr ""

#: .\Modification_Files\NPC\v_npc_responds\Isolated\v_lo_responses.json
msgid "So, where do I find this place?"
msgstr ""

#: .\Modification_Files\NPC\v_npc_responds\Isolated\v_lo_responses.json
msgid ""
"Do not bring me to my death. I will leave MY territory and expect benefits "
"believing in you."
msgstr ""

#: .\Modification_Files\NPC\v_npc_responds\Isolated\v_lo_responses.json
msgid "I promise..."
msgstr ""

#: .\Modification_Files\NPC\v_npc_responds\Isolated\v_lo_responses.json
msgid "I already said I refuse... NOW, I have to kill you for your ignorance!"
msgstr ""

#: .\Modification_Files\NPC\v_npc_responds\Isolated\v_lo_responses.json
msgid "KILL ME IF YOU CAN!!!"
msgstr ""

#: .\Modification_Files\NPC\v_npc_responds\Isolated\v_lo_responses.json
msgid "These places could be anywhere far from human civilizations."
msgstr ""

#: .\Modification_Files\NPC\v_npc_responds\Isolated\v_lo_responses.json
msgid "Nope. Even if I know, I won't tell you."
msgstr ""

#: .\Modification_Files\NPC\v_npc_responds\Isolated\v_lo_responses.json
msgid "Thanks, I guess..."
msgstr ""

#: .\Modification_Files\NPC\v_npc_responds\Isolated\v_lo_responses.json
msgid "You sure about that?"
msgstr ""

#: .\Modification_Files\NPC\v_npc_responds\Isolated\v_lo_responses.json
msgid "Yes, I do."
msgstr ""

#: .\Modification_Files\NPC\v_npc_responds\Isolated\v_lo_responses.json
msgid "I take back what I've said..."
msgstr ""

#: .\Modification_Files\NPC\v_npc_responds\Isolated\v_lo_responses.json
msgid ""
"No, I have no more requests for you. You have helped me alot and proven me "
"your worth. As a reward, I'll give you my mark of trust on you."
msgstr ""

#: .\Modification_Files\NPC\v_npc_responds\Isolated\v_lo_responses.json
msgid "Thank you for this mark... Let's go!"
msgstr ""

#: .\Modification_Files\NPC\v_npc_responds\Isolated\v_lo_responses.json
msgid ""
"You think I'm foolish to believe you as my kind? Trust me, mortal, us "
"vampires are not born by drinking artificial drugs."
msgstr ""

#: .\Modification_Files\NPC\v_npc_responds\Isolated\v_lo_responses.json
msgid "Well, atleast I'm alot stronger than you."
msgstr ""

#: .\Modification_Files\NPC\v_npc_responds\Underrefugee\v_uc_responses.json
msgid "Here's your small leech teeth."
msgstr ""

#: .\Modification_Files\NPC\v_npc_responds\Underrefugee\v_uc_responses.json
msgid "Here's your blood sac."
msgstr ""

#: .\Modification_Files\NPC\v_npc_responds\Underrefugee\v_uc_responses.json
msgid "You got something to say, descendant?."
msgstr ""

#: .\Modification_Files\NPC\v_npc_responds\Underrefugee\v_uc_responses.json
msgid "Mortal descendant... What do I expect from you?"
msgstr ""

#: .\Modification_Files\NPC\v_npc_responds\Underrefugee\v_uc_responses.json
msgid "I want to talk with you."
msgstr ""

#: .\Modification_Files\NPC\v_npc_responds\Underrefugee\v_uc_responses.json
msgid "Any work can I do?."
msgstr ""

#: .\Modification_Files\NPC\v_npc_responds\Underrefugee\v_uc_responses.json
msgid "I've done the final test... So, what now?"
msgstr ""

#: .\Modification_Files\NPC\v_npc_responds\Underrefugee\v_uc_responses.json
msgid "About your command..."
msgstr ""

#: .\Modification_Files\NPC\v_npc_responds\Underrefugee\v_uc_responses.json
msgid "I should go now."
msgstr ""

#: .\Modification_Files\NPC\v_npc_responds\Underrefugee\v_uc_responses.json
msgid "So descendant... What should we talk about?"
msgstr ""

#: .\Modification_Files\NPC\v_npc_responds\Underrefugee\v_uc_responses.json
msgid "Topic?"
msgstr ""

#: .\Modification_Files\NPC\v_npc_responds\Underrefugee\v_uc_responses.json
#: .\Modification_Files\NPC\v_npc_responds\Underrefugee\v_us_responses.json
#: .\Modification_Files\NPC\v_npc_responds\Underrefugee\v_ut_responses.json
#: .\Modification_Files\NPC\v_npc_responds\Wastelands_Outskirts\v_vgs_responses.json
#: .\Modification_Files\NPC\v_npc_responds\Wastelands_Outskirts\v_wg2_responses.json
msgid "Who are you?"
msgstr ""

#: .\Modification_Files\NPC\v_npc_responds\Underrefugee\v_uc_responses.json
msgid "Wait... Vampire with a gun?"
msgstr ""

#: .\Modification_Files\NPC\v_npc_responds\Underrefugee\v_uc_responses.json
msgid "News about the outside world, sir?"
msgstr ""

#: .\Modification_Files\NPC\v_npc_responds\Underrefugee\v_uc_responses.json
msgid "Do you offer your guns in trading?"
msgstr ""

#: .\Modification_Files\NPC\v_npc_responds\Underrefugee\v_uc_responses.json
msgid "Let's talk later."
msgstr ""

#: .\Modification_Files\NPC\v_npc_responds\Underrefugee\v_uc_responses.json
msgid "I guess I've asked everything..."
msgstr ""

#: .\Modification_Files\NPC\v_npc_responds\Underrefugee\v_uc_responses.json
msgid "I am a vampire, guarding this place from any kinds of threat."
msgstr ""

#: .\Modification_Files\NPC\v_npc_responds\Underrefugee\v_uc_responses.json
msgid "So, are you the owner of this refugee?"
msgstr ""

#: .\Modification_Files\NPC\v_npc_responds\Underrefugee\v_uc_responses.json
msgid "Sorry about it..."
msgstr ""

#: .\Modification_Files\NPC\v_npc_responds\Underrefugee\v_uc_responses.json
msgid "You thought we can't use this things? You are wrong, descendant!"
msgstr ""

#: .\Modification_Files\NPC\v_npc_responds\Underrefugee\v_uc_responses.json
msgid "Umm... Okay."
msgstr ""

#: .\Modification_Files\NPC\v_npc_responds\Underrefugee\v_uc_responses.json
msgid "I have no idea. Its been decades since I traveled into this cove."
msgstr ""

#: .\Modification_Files\NPC\v_npc_responds\Underrefugee\v_uc_responses.json
msgid "Oh. Okay."
msgstr ""

#: .\Modification_Files\NPC\v_npc_responds\Underrefugee\v_uc_responses.json
msgid "Nope. To trade a gun like this, you better find a gunshop."
msgstr ""

#: .\Modification_Files\NPC\v_npc_responds\Underrefugee\v_uc_responses.json
msgid "A gunshop?"
msgstr ""

#: .\Modification_Files\NPC\v_npc_responds\Underrefugee\v_uc_responses.json
msgid "No. This is owned and built by HIM."
msgstr ""

#: .\Modification_Files\NPC\v_npc_responds\Underrefugee\v_uc_responses.json
msgid "Who is HIM?"
msgstr ""

#: .\Modification_Files\NPC\v_npc_responds\Underrefugee\v_uc_responses.json
msgid ""
"She's at the wasteland outskirts, a place where vampires freely communicate "
"with you all. Sounds wonderful, right?"
msgstr ""

#: .\Modification_Files\NPC\v_npc_responds\Underrefugee\v_uc_responses.json
msgid "Wonderful? I don't even know where it is!"
msgstr ""

#: .\Modification_Files\NPC\v_npc_responds\Underrefugee\v_uc_responses.json
msgid ""
"HIM is our master, our lord, the almighty one. HE brought us into existence,"
" and we owe our life serving HIS will."
msgstr ""

#: .\Modification_Files\NPC\v_npc_responds\Underrefugee\v_uc_responses.json
msgid "I'd wish to meet HIM..."
msgstr ""

#: .\Modification_Files\NPC\v_npc_responds\Underrefugee\v_uc_responses.json
msgid ""
"\"What now\" you say? The tests I have given you has to proven yourself "
"worthy to push forward the boundary between this cave and the outskirt. Now,"
" take this ring and tell the seeker about the outskirts, she'll talk about "
"and guide you to its coordinates. The gunshop has something to give when you"
" arrive, so make sure you wear the ring before speaking to her."
msgstr ""

#: .\Modification_Files\NPC\v_npc_responds\Underrefugee\v_uc_responses.json
msgid "Yes. I'll do as you say and thank you for this ring."
msgstr ""

#: .\Modification_Files\NPC\v_npc_responds\Underrefugee\v_ug_responses.json
msgid "You look important."
msgstr ""

#: .\Modification_Files\NPC\v_npc_responds\Underrefugee\v_ug_responses.json
msgid "Mortal... You're up to nothing?"
msgstr ""

#: .\Modification_Files\NPC\v_npc_responds\Underrefugee\v_ug_responses.json
#: .\Modification_Files\NPC\v_npc_responds\Wastelands_Outskirts\v_wg2_responses.json
msgid "Where am I?"
msgstr ""

#: .\Modification_Files\NPC\v_npc_responds\Underrefugee\v_ug_responses.json
#: .\Modification_Files\NPC\v_npc_responds\Underrefugee\v_us_responses.json
msgid "I'd be going now..."
msgstr ""

#: .\Modification_Files\NPC\v_npc_responds\Underrefugee\v_ug_responses.json
msgid "Just an assigned guard here, nothing happened 'till you came in."
msgstr ""

#: .\Modification_Files\NPC\v_npc_responds\Underrefugee\v_ug_responses.json
msgid "Why should I? If you want answers, go ask my partner."
msgstr ""

#: .\Modification_Files\NPC\v_npc_responds\Underrefugee\v_ug_responses.json
msgid "I like you."
msgstr ""

#: .\Modification_Files\NPC\v_npc_responds\Underrefugee\v_ug_responses.json
msgid "You think I'm a dummy? Stop repeating your question, kid!"
msgstr ""

#: .\Modification_Files\NPC\v_npc_responds\Underrefugee\v_ug_responses.json
#: .\Modification_Files\NPC\v_npc_responds\Wastelands_Outskirts\v_vgs_responses.json
msgid "Sorry..."
msgstr ""

#: .\Modification_Files\NPC\v_npc_responds\Underrefugee\v_ug_responses.json
msgid "I know you know where you are. *grins*."
msgstr ""

#: .\Modification_Files\NPC\v_npc_responds\Underrefugee\v_ug_responses.json
msgid "Geez, don't show that to me."
msgstr ""

#: .\Modification_Files\NPC\v_npc_responds\Underrefugee\v_ug_responses.json
msgid "Okay, okay."
msgstr ""

#: .\Modification_Files\NPC\v_npc_responds\Underrefugee\v_ug_responses.json
msgid "Now I know where we are."
msgstr ""

#: .\Modification_Files\NPC\v_npc_responds\Underrefugee\v_ug_responses.json
msgid "Shut up mortal, everyone does like me."
msgstr ""

#: .\Modification_Files\NPC\v_npc_responds\Underrefugee\v_ug_responses.json
msgid "Oh..."
msgstr ""

#: .\Modification_Files\NPC\v_npc_responds\Underrefugee\v_ug_responses.json
msgid "If you're here to fuck us up, I'd really need to slay you immediately!"
msgstr ""

#: .\Modification_Files\NPC\v_npc_responds\Underrefugee\v_ug_responses.json
msgid "I apologize for my mistake."
msgstr ""

#: .\Modification_Files\NPC\v_npc_responds\Underrefugee\v_ug_responses.json
msgid "YEAH GIRL! BRING IT!"
msgstr ""

#: .\Modification_Files\NPC\v_npc_responds\Underrefugee\v_ug_responses.json
msgid "Damn, you managed to wear that."
msgstr ""

#: .\Modification_Files\NPC\v_npc_responds\Underrefugee\v_ug_responses.json
msgid "Mortal, You look dazzled?"
msgstr ""

#: .\Modification_Files\NPC\v_npc_responds\Underrefugee\v_ug_responses.json
msgid "Tell me who you are."
msgstr ""

#: .\Modification_Files\NPC\v_npc_responds\Underrefugee\v_ug_responses.json
msgid "I'm vacant for jobs."
msgstr ""

#: .\Modification_Files\NPC\v_npc_responds\Underrefugee\v_ug_responses.json
msgid "Bye..."
msgstr ""

#: .\Modification_Files\NPC\v_npc_responds\Underrefugee\v_ug_responses.json
msgid "I don't actually have a problem, but others could have."
msgstr ""

#: .\Modification_Files\NPC\v_npc_responds\Underrefugee\v_ug_responses.json
msgid "I'll ask them."
msgstr ""

#: .\Modification_Files\NPC\v_npc_responds\Underrefugee\v_ug_responses.json
msgid "I'm a guardian, defending our cave from unwelcome intruders like you."
msgstr ""

#: .\Modification_Files\NPC\v_npc_responds\Underrefugee\v_ug_responses.json
msgid "Whoa, I'm not here to pick fights."
msgstr ""

#: .\Modification_Files\NPC\v_npc_responds\Underrefugee\v_ug_responses.json
msgid "Nice..."
msgstr ""

#: .\Modification_Files\NPC\v_npc_responds\Underrefugee\v_ug_responses.json
msgid ""
"You're on the vampire cove, a refugee itself. This is our place with peace "
"and sure living for centuries for us all. After that magical outbreak, we "
"are forced to eat and drink certain foodstuff like animal meat chunks and "
"its blood, but we never tried to consume rotten flesh from those frenzied "
"humans."
msgstr ""

#: .\Modification_Files\NPC\v_npc_responds\Underrefugee\v_ug_responses.json
msgid "It's not magical, it's Cataclysm."
msgstr ""

#: .\Modification_Files\NPC\v_npc_responds\Underrefugee\v_ug_responses.json
msgid "Oh great."
msgstr ""

#: .\Modification_Files\NPC\v_npc_responds\Underrefugee\v_ug_responses.json
msgid ""
"You should be. We never, EVER let any humans come into our beloved home. "
"Until we are commanded to accompany with your kind."
msgstr ""

#: .\Modification_Files\NPC\v_npc_responds\Underrefugee\v_ug_responses.json
msgid "Who commanded you?"
msgstr ""

#: .\Modification_Files\NPC\v_npc_responds\Underrefugee\v_ug_responses.json
msgid "Oh... Seems you are forced to talk with me."
msgstr ""

#: .\Modification_Files\NPC\v_npc_responds\Underrefugee\v_ug_responses.json
msgid ""
"Cataclysm? So you humans made those thingies... Well, I can't blame you for "
"that."
msgstr ""

#: .\Modification_Files\NPC\v_npc_responds\Underrefugee\v_ug_responses.json
msgid "You're right..."
msgstr ""

#: .\Modification_Files\NPC\v_npc_responds\Underrefugee\v_ug_responses.json
msgid ""
"You look concerned, but I'll never let a word come out from my mouth about "
"HIM."
msgstr ""

#: .\Modification_Files\NPC\v_npc_responds\Underrefugee\v_ug_responses.json
msgid "Never knew you're loyal..."
msgstr ""

#: .\Modification_Files\NPC\v_npc_responds\Underrefugee\v_ug_responses.json
msgid "What do you need?."
msgstr ""

#: .\Modification_Files\NPC\v_npc_responds\Underrefugee\v_ug_responses.json
#: .\Modification_Files\NPC\v_npc_responds\Wastelands_Outskirts\v_vgs_responses.json
msgid "Nothing..."
msgstr ""

#: .\Modification_Files\NPC\v_npc_responds\Underrefugee\v_ug_responses.json
#: .\Modification_Files\NPC\v_npc_responds\Wastelands_Outskirts\h_wr2_responses.json
msgid "What are you doing here?"
msgstr ""

#: .\Modification_Files\NPC\v_npc_responds\Underrefugee\v_ug_responses.json
msgid "I was tasked to watch over the two rampaging kindreds in their cages."
msgstr ""

#: .\Modification_Files\NPC\v_npc_responds\Underrefugee\v_ug_responses.json
#: .\Modification_Files\NPC\v_npc_responds\Wastelands_Outskirts\h_wr1_responses.json
#: .\Modification_Files\NPC\v_npc_responds\Wastelands_Outskirts\v_wg2_responses.json
msgid "Oh, okay..."
msgstr ""

#: .\Modification_Files\NPC\v_npc_responds\Underrefugee\v_ug_responses.json
msgid "May I kill those two vampires?."
msgstr ""

#: .\Modification_Files\NPC\v_npc_responds\Underrefugee\v_ug_responses.json
msgid ""
"Ofcourse, you can! We already have lost our faith on them to fight back "
"their rabid sickness."
msgstr ""

#: .\Modification_Files\NPC\v_npc_responds\Underrefugee\v_ug_responses.json
msgid "That's too bad..."
msgstr ""

#: .\Modification_Files\NPC\v_npc_responds\Underrefugee\v_ug_responses.json
msgid "Just staying in the darkness... Away from the horrifying magic."
msgstr ""

#: .\Modification_Files\NPC\v_npc_responds\Underrefugee\v_ug_responses.json
msgid "I guess you're afraid of Cataclysm..."
msgstr ""

#: .\Modification_Files\NPC\v_npc_responds\Underrefugee\v_us_responses.json
msgid "Can you tell me who you are?"
msgstr ""

#: .\Modification_Files\NPC\v_npc_responds\Underrefugee\v_us_responses.json
msgid "About our journey..."
msgstr ""

#: .\Modification_Files\NPC\v_npc_responds\Underrefugee\v_us_responses.json
msgid "Jobs to work?"
msgstr ""

#: .\Modification_Files\NPC\v_npc_responds\Underrefugee\v_us_responses.json
msgid "They've let me help in their troubles."
msgstr ""

#: .\Modification_Files\NPC\v_npc_responds\Underrefugee\v_us_responses.json
msgid "We need to go to the vampirus."
msgstr ""

#: .\Modification_Files\NPC\v_npc_responds\Underrefugee\v_us_responses.json
msgid "About our job..."
msgstr ""

#: .\Modification_Files\NPC\v_npc_responds\Underrefugee\v_us_responses.json
msgid "...?"
msgstr ""

#: .\Modification_Files\NPC\v_npc_responds\Underrefugee\v_us_responses.json
msgid ""
"I see you've been working hard to help us on our problems... Nice meeting "
"you and I apologize for ignoring you from the start I glanced on your eyes."
msgstr ""

#: .\Modification_Files\NPC\v_npc_responds\Underrefugee\v_us_responses.json
msgid "As I was saying..."
msgstr ""

#: .\Modification_Files\NPC\v_npc_responds\Underrefugee\v_us_responses.json
msgid ""
"I am the seeker of this cave, and my job is to scout the surrounding areas "
"for possible threats."
msgstr ""

#: .\Modification_Files\NPC\v_npc_responds\Underrefugee\v_us_responses.json
msgid "What kind of threats?"
msgstr ""

#: .\Modification_Files\NPC\v_npc_responds\Underrefugee\v_us_responses.json
#: .\Modification_Files\NPC\v_npc_responds\Underrefugee\v_ut_responses.json
#: .\Modification_Files\NPC\v_npc_responds\Wastelands_Outskirts\h_wr1_responses.json
#: .\Modification_Files\NPC\v_npc_responds\Wastelands_Outskirts\v_wg1_responses.json
#: .\Modification_Files\NPC\v_npc_responds\Wastelands_Outskirts\v_wg2_responses.json
msgid "Okay..."
msgstr ""

#: .\Modification_Files\NPC\v_npc_responds\Underrefugee\v_us_responses.json
msgid "Nothing dangerous, its all the same everytime."
msgstr ""

#: .\Modification_Files\NPC\v_npc_responds\Underrefugee\v_us_responses.json
msgid "Well, okay."
msgstr ""

#: .\Modification_Files\NPC\v_npc_responds\Underrefugee\v_us_responses.json
msgid ""
"Good. If you need me to come along, just tell me and I will help you in your"
" troubles."
msgstr ""

#: .\Modification_Files\NPC\v_npc_responds\Underrefugee\v_us_responses.json
msgid "Come with me."
msgstr ""

#: .\Modification_Files\NPC\v_npc_responds\Underrefugee\v_us_responses.json
msgid "Job's too easy to bring you along."
msgstr ""

#: .\Modification_Files\NPC\v_npc_responds\Underrefugee\v_us_responses.json
msgid "Lead the way, descendant."
msgstr ""

#: .\Modification_Files\NPC\v_npc_responds\Underrefugee\v_us_responses.json
msgid "Let's go!"
msgstr ""

#: .\Modification_Files\NPC\v_npc_responds\Underrefugee\v_us_responses.json
msgid "As you say, descendant..."
msgstr ""

#: .\Modification_Files\NPC\v_npc_responds\Underrefugee\v_us_responses.json
#: .\Modification_Files\NPC\v_npc_responds\Wastelands_Outskirts\h_wjs_responses.json
#: .\Modification_Files\NPC\v_npc_responds\Wastelands_Outskirts\h_wr1_responses.json
#: .\Modification_Files\NPC\v_npc_responds\Wastelands_Outskirts\h_wr2_responses.json
#: .\Modification_Files\NPC\v_npc_responds\Wastelands_Outskirts\h_wrs_responses.json
msgid "Bye."
msgstr ""

#: .\Modification_Files\NPC\v_npc_responds\Underrefugee\v_us_responses.json
msgid "Descendant, are you sure about this?"
msgstr ""

#: .\Modification_Files\NPC\v_npc_responds\Underrefugee\v_us_responses.json
#: .\Modification_Files\NPC\v_npc_responds\Vampirus\h_prison_cell.json
#: .\Modification_Files\NPC\v_npc_responds\Wastelands_Outskirts\v_wg1_responses.json
msgid "Yes."
msgstr ""

#: .\Modification_Files\NPC\v_npc_responds\Underrefugee\v_us_responses.json
msgid "Tell me the problem, descendant."
msgstr ""

#: .\Modification_Files\NPC\v_npc_responds\Underrefugee\v_us_responses.json
msgid "We can't go down the slope."
msgstr ""

#: .\Modification_Files\NPC\v_npc_responds\Underrefugee\v_us_responses.json
msgid "Nevermind..."
msgstr ""

#: .\Modification_Files\NPC\v_npc_responds\Underrefugee\v_us_responses.json
msgid "Doing this job takes time..."
msgstr ""

#: .\Modification_Files\NPC\v_npc_responds\Underrefugee\v_us_responses.json
msgid ""
"Hmm, these bastards has sealed the entrance. I didn't expect for them to use"
" a spell, even tho they're heavily influenced by the magic..."
msgstr ""

#: .\Modification_Files\NPC\v_npc_responds\Underrefugee\v_us_responses.json
msgid "So, can you unseal the entrance?"
msgstr ""

#: .\Modification_Files\NPC\v_npc_responds\Underrefugee\v_us_responses.json
msgid "I must perform this at night by the entrance."
msgstr ""

#: .\Modification_Files\NPC\v_npc_responds\Underrefugee\v_ut_responses.json
msgid "Here's your corrupted bloodrune stones."
msgstr ""

#: .\Modification_Files\NPC\v_npc_responds\Underrefugee\v_ut_responses.json
msgid "Do you need something, mortal?."
msgstr ""

#: .\Modification_Files\NPC\v_npc_responds\Underrefugee\v_ut_responses.json
msgid "Want something?"
msgstr ""

#: .\Modification_Files\NPC\v_npc_responds\Underrefugee\v_ut_responses.json
msgid "Tell me what happened outside."
msgstr ""

#: .\Modification_Files\NPC\v_npc_responds\Underrefugee\v_ut_responses.json
msgid "I'll trade with ya..."
msgstr ""

#: .\Modification_Files\NPC\v_npc_responds\Underrefugee\v_ut_responses.json
msgid "You need help? I'm here to do it."
msgstr ""

#: .\Modification_Files\NPC\v_npc_responds\Underrefugee\v_ut_responses.json
msgid "About your quest..."
msgstr ""

#: .\Modification_Files\NPC\v_npc_responds\Underrefugee\v_ut_responses.json
msgid "Bye, see you later."
msgstr ""

#: .\Modification_Files\NPC\v_npc_responds\Underrefugee\v_ut_responses.json
msgid ""
"I am assigned as a trader by my master. I sell our artifact materials used "
"in forging vampiric stuff. Or buy an already forged ones for a higher trade "
"value."
msgstr ""

#: .\Modification_Files\NPC\v_npc_responds\Underrefugee\v_ut_responses.json
msgid "Wait. Why are you selling artifacts?"
msgstr ""

#: .\Modification_Files\NPC\v_npc_responds\Underrefugee\v_ut_responses.json
msgid "Why the hell are you accepting human stuff in trading?"
msgstr ""

#: .\Modification_Files\NPC\v_npc_responds\Underrefugee\v_ut_responses.json
msgid "Okay!."
msgstr ""

#: .\Modification_Files\NPC\v_npc_responds\Underrefugee\v_ut_responses.json
msgid ""
"I have no idea what's happening outside right now. I came here without "
"sunburn after taking orders from HIM."
msgstr ""

#: .\Modification_Files\NPC\v_npc_responds\Underrefugee\v_ut_responses.json
msgid "Well, I expected nothing..."
msgstr ""

#: .\Modification_Files\NPC\v_npc_responds\Underrefugee\v_ut_responses.json
msgid ""
"Our master wants to help the last, surviving humans in our utmost "
"solution... Share our power with you all. But he still wants an official "
"trading, so you need lots of valuables or cash buying our items."
msgstr ""

#: .\Modification_Files\NPC\v_npc_responds\Underrefugee\v_ut_responses.json
msgid "Oh... Just great."
msgstr ""

#: .\Modification_Files\NPC\v_npc_responds\Underrefugee\v_ut_responses.json
msgid ""
"I don't know. Our master said we have to accept any valuables you humans got"
" in your trip."
msgstr ""

#: .\Modification_Files\NPC\v_npc_responds\Underrefugee\v_ut_responses.json
msgid "Master? Could you tell me anything about this HIM?"
msgstr ""

#: .\Modification_Files\NPC\v_npc_responds\Underrefugee\v_ut_responses.json
msgid "Nope. HE remains a mystery to all of you."
msgstr ""

#: .\Modification_Files\NPC\v_npc_responds\Underrefugee\v_ut_responses.json
msgid "Damn... You can't tell even HIS face."
msgstr ""

#: .\Modification_Files\NPC\v_npc_responds\Underrefugee\v_ut_responses.json
msgid ""
"HIM is our master, the reason of our immortality and existence in this "
"damned world."
msgstr ""

#: .\Modification_Files\NPC\v_npc_responds\Underrefugee\v_ut_responses.json
msgid "So, where is HE?"
msgstr ""

#: .\Modification_Files\NPC\v_npc_responds\Underrefugee\v_ut_responses.json
msgid "Don't even try to know..."
msgstr ""

#: .\Modification_Files\NPC\v_npc_responds\Underrefugee\v_ut_responses.json
msgid "No. I guess those problems are enough to help us out..."
msgstr ""

#: .\Modification_Files\NPC\v_npc_responds\Vampirus\h_prison_cell.json
msgid "Are you done?"
msgstr ""

#: .\Modification_Files\NPC\v_npc_responds\Vampirus\h_prison_cell.json
msgid "Please help me... They... they're so... cruel..."
msgstr ""

#: .\Modification_Files\NPC\v_npc_responds\Vampirus\h_prison_cell.json
msgid ""
"Damn... those suckers... please I beg you to...\n"
"*cough*"
msgstr ""

#: .\Modification_Files\NPC\v_npc_responds\Vampirus\h_prison_cell.json
msgid ""
"COME CLOSER OR I-I'LL... damn these <swear> suckers really took a piece out "
"of my sanity."
msgstr ""

#: .\Modification_Files\NPC\v_npc_responds\Vampirus\h_prison_cell.json
msgid "TOUCH ME AND I'LL!... oh... you're not a monster..."
msgstr ""

#: .\Modification_Files\NPC\v_npc_responds\Vampirus\h_prison_cell.json
msgid "It's okay, I'm here to set you free."
msgstr ""

#: .\Modification_Files\NPC\v_npc_responds\Vampirus\h_prison_cell.json
msgid "Sorry, I can't help you out. I have things to deal with."
msgstr ""

#: .\Modification_Files\NPC\v_npc_responds\Vampirus\h_prison_cell.json
msgid "I don't take a weakling along with me. Now run."
msgstr ""

#: .\Modification_Files\NPC\v_npc_responds\Vampirus\h_prison_cell.json
msgid "Bye? I guess..."
msgstr ""

#: .\Modification_Files\NPC\v_npc_responds\Vampirus\h_prison_cell.json
msgid "Not yet..."
msgstr ""

#: .\Modification_Files\NPC\v_npc_responds\Vampirus\h_prison_cell.json
msgid "Thank you so much!... But where do we go?"
msgstr ""

#: .\Modification_Files\NPC\v_npc_responds\Vampirus\h_prison_cell.json
msgid "To the wasteland outskirts."
msgstr ""

#: .\Modification_Files\NPC\v_npc_responds\Vampirus\h_prison_cell.json
msgid "I don't know, but stick with me and you'll be safe."
msgstr ""

#: .\Modification_Files\NPC\v_npc_responds\Vampirus\h_prison_cell.json
msgid "Sounds cool!"
msgstr ""

#: .\Modification_Files\NPC\v_npc_responds\Vampirus\h_prison_cell.json
msgid "Yes it is..."
msgstr ""

#: .\Modification_Files\NPC\v_npc_responds\Vampirus\h_prison_cell.json
msgid "I owe my life to your kindness so... Lets go!"
msgstr ""

#: .\Modification_Files\NPC\v_npc_responds\Vampirus\h_prison_cell.json
msgid "We go!"
msgstr ""

#: .\Modification_Files\NPC\v_npc_responds\Vampirus\h_prison_cell.json
msgid ""
"Wait! What if we help each other! I mean, I'll come assist you and set me "
"free after!"
msgstr ""

#: .\Modification_Files\NPC\v_npc_responds\Vampirus\h_prison_cell.json
msgid "You're too weak to fight them."
msgstr ""

#: .\Modification_Files\NPC\v_npc_responds\Vampirus\h_prison_cell.json
msgid "Or just wait here and we'll get you out later."
msgstr ""

#: .\Modification_Files\NPC\v_npc_responds\Vampirus\h_prison_cell.json
msgid "Does that mean I can't leave this place?"
msgstr ""

#: .\Modification_Files\NPC\v_npc_responds\Vampirus\h_prison_cell.json
msgid "Yea- I mean, never!"
msgstr ""

#: .\Modification_Files\NPC\v_npc_responds\Vampirus\h_prison_cell.json
msgid "Yeah, but we'll be back to help you out."
msgstr ""

#: .\Modification_Files\NPC\v_npc_responds\Vampirus\h_prison_cell.json
msgid "Thank you! I'll expect for you to come for me after this mess."
msgstr ""

#: .\Modification_Files\NPC\v_npc_responds\Vampirus\h_prison_cell.json
msgid "See you later."
msgstr ""

#: .\Modification_Files\NPC\v_npc_responds\Vampirus\h_prison_cell.json
msgid "Thank goodness! Please take me out of here."
msgstr ""

#: .\Modification_Files\NPC\v_npc_responds\Vampirus\h_prison_cell.json
msgid "Not to be rude or anything but... Where will you take me to?"
msgstr ""

#: .\Modification_Files\NPC\v_npc_responds\Vampirus\h_prison_cell.json
msgid "After beating those monsters, I know you're too strong to protect me!"
msgstr ""

#: .\Modification_Files\NPC\v_npc_responds\Vampirus\h_prison_cell.json
msgid "Well... Don't be timid to your belief."
msgstr ""

#: .\Modification_Files\NPC\v_npc_responds\Wastelands_Outskirts\h_wjs_responses.json
msgid "Good to see ya, bud!"
msgstr ""

#: .\Modification_Files\NPC\v_npc_responds\Wastelands_Outskirts\h_wjs_responses.json
msgid "Hello there traveler!"
msgstr ""

#: .\Modification_Files\NPC\v_npc_responds\Wastelands_Outskirts\h_wjs_responses.json
msgid "Interested in my wares?!"
msgstr ""

#: .\Modification_Files\NPC\v_npc_responds\Wastelands_Outskirts\h_wjs_responses.json
msgid "Who and what are you doing here?."
msgstr ""

#: .\Modification_Files\NPC\v_npc_responds\Wastelands_Outskirts\h_wjs_responses.json
msgid "Any job to offer?."
msgstr ""

#: .\Modification_Files\NPC\v_npc_responds\Wastelands_Outskirts\h_wjs_responses.json
msgid "I want your junk..."
msgstr ""

#: .\Modification_Files\NPC\v_npc_responds\Wastelands_Outskirts\h_wjs_responses.json
msgid ""
"Just a silly guy collecting garbage outside, somewhere far from those "
"frenzied walkers. There are times my job put me into risks, so I only bring "
"few of them back here."
msgstr ""

#: .\Modification_Files\NPC\v_npc_responds\Wastelands_Outskirts\h_wjs_responses.json
msgid "And... How's the living here?"
msgstr ""

#: .\Modification_Files\NPC\v_npc_responds\Wastelands_Outskirts\h_wjs_responses.json
msgid ""
"Peaceful as always. But you see, life's been easier living along with these "
"vampires. They offer us protection from all sorts of threat while us humans "
"do the usual chores outside."
msgstr ""

#: .\Modification_Files\NPC\v_npc_responds\Wastelands_Outskirts\h_wjs_responses.json
msgid "I guess they're friendly afterall..."
msgstr ""

#: .\Modification_Files\NPC\v_npc_responds\Wastelands_Outskirts\h_wjs_responses.json
msgid ""
"I have said my words clearly, or you like to repeat one's answer for fun?"
msgstr ""

#: .\Modification_Files\NPC\v_npc_responds\Wastelands_Outskirts\h_wjs_responses.json
msgid "Sorry about that..."
msgstr ""

#: .\Modification_Files\NPC\v_npc_responds\Wastelands_Outskirts\h_wjs_responses.json
msgid ""
"Hey buddy, I sell stuff here. Do you think I have a problem?\n"
"*Points a finger to his face*"
msgstr ""

#: .\Modification_Files\NPC\v_npc_responds\Wastelands_Outskirts\h_wjs_responses.json
msgid "Ummm... No."
msgstr ""

#: .\Modification_Files\NPC\v_npc_responds\Wastelands_Outskirts\h_wr1_responses.json
msgid "Hey, what's up?"
msgstr ""

#: .\Modification_Files\NPC\v_npc_responds\Wastelands_Outskirts\h_wr1_responses.json
msgid "What's happening here?."
msgstr ""

#: .\Modification_Files\NPC\v_npc_responds\Wastelands_Outskirts\h_wr1_responses.json
msgid "Want to come along?."
msgstr ""

#: .\Modification_Files\NPC\v_npc_responds\Wastelands_Outskirts\h_wr1_responses.json
msgid "As usual. Repairs, gatherings, carnages... "
msgstr ""

#: .\Modification_Files\NPC\v_npc_responds\Wastelands_Outskirts\h_wr1_responses.json
msgid "Are you sure about this? I could be a burden in your travels?"
msgstr ""

#: .\Modification_Files\NPC\v_npc_responds\Wastelands_Outskirts\h_wr1_responses.json
msgid "I don't say I don't trust you, but no."
msgstr ""

#: .\Modification_Files\NPC\v_npc_responds\Wastelands_Outskirts\h_wr1_responses.json
msgid "Just follow me and we'll be fine."
msgstr ""

#: .\Modification_Files\NPC\v_npc_responds\Wastelands_Outskirts\h_wr1_responses.json
msgid "Just kiddin'."
msgstr ""

#: .\Modification_Files\NPC\v_npc_responds\Wastelands_Outskirts\h_wr1_responses.json
msgid "Bye then..."
msgstr ""

#: .\Modification_Files\NPC\v_npc_responds\Wastelands_Outskirts\h_wr2_responses.json
msgid "Hello outsider"
msgstr ""

#: .\Modification_Files\NPC\v_npc_responds\Wastelands_Outskirts\h_wr2_responses.json
msgid "I want to talk."
msgstr ""

#: .\Modification_Files\NPC\v_npc_responds\Wastelands_Outskirts\h_wr2_responses.json
msgid "Hi and bye."
msgstr ""

#: .\Modification_Files\NPC\v_npc_responds\Wastelands_Outskirts\h_wr2_responses.json
msgid "About what?"
msgstr ""

#: .\Modification_Files\NPC\v_npc_responds\Wastelands_Outskirts\h_wr2_responses.json
msgid "Got a problem?"
msgstr ""

#: .\Modification_Files\NPC\v_npc_responds\Wastelands_Outskirts\h_wr2_responses.json
msgid ""
"I guard here, most of the time. But sometimes I do few things other than "
"that."
msgstr ""

#: .\Modification_Files\NPC\v_npc_responds\Wastelands_Outskirts\h_wr2_responses.json
msgid "Got it."
msgstr ""

#: .\Modification_Files\NPC\v_npc_responds\Wastelands_Outskirts\h_wr2_responses.json
msgid "Nope."
msgstr ""

#: .\Modification_Files\NPC\v_npc_responds\Wastelands_Outskirts\h_wr2_responses.json
msgid "You said it..."
msgstr ""

#: .\Modification_Files\NPC\v_npc_responds\Wastelands_Outskirts\h_wrs_responses.json
msgid "Bye now..."
msgstr ""

#: .\Modification_Files\NPC\v_npc_responds\Wastelands_Outskirts\h_wrs_responses.json
msgid ""
"Don't waste your time talking to me at this point, just focus on the road!"
msgstr ""

#: .\Modification_Files\NPC\v_npc_responds\Wastelands_Outskirts\h_wrs_responses.json
msgid "Are you going to bring me there now?"
msgstr ""

#: .\Modification_Files\NPC\v_npc_responds\Wastelands_Outskirts\h_wrs_responses.json
msgid ""
"Well hi there? Its been a while since I see a living human walking in this "
"damned world!"
msgstr ""

#: .\Modification_Files\NPC\v_npc_responds\Wastelands_Outskirts\h_wrs_responses.json
msgid "We need your help in operating a radio tower."
msgstr ""

#: .\Modification_Files\NPC\v_npc_responds\Wastelands_Outskirts\h_wrs_responses.json
msgid "Yes. I will."
msgstr ""

#: .\Modification_Files\NPC\v_npc_responds\Wastelands_Outskirts\h_wrs_responses.json
msgid "Okay! I'll do it!"
msgstr ""

#: .\Modification_Files\NPC\v_npc_responds\Wastelands_Outskirts\h_wrs_responses.json
msgid "Radios are too simple to use, why'd would you want me to do it myself?"
msgstr ""

#: .\Modification_Files\NPC\v_npc_responds\Wastelands_Outskirts\h_wrs_responses.json
msgid "To ease the job?"
msgstr ""

#: .\Modification_Files\NPC\v_npc_responds\Wastelands_Outskirts\h_wrs_responses.json
msgid "Increase the efficiency of our radio?"
msgstr ""

#: .\Modification_Files\NPC\v_npc_responds\Wastelands_Outskirts\h_wrs_responses.json
msgid "Its a complicated thing for us..."
msgstr ""

#: .\Modification_Files\NPC\v_npc_responds\Wastelands_Outskirts\h_wrs_responses.json
msgid "We better get going."
msgstr ""

#: .\Modification_Files\NPC\v_npc_responds\Wastelands_Outskirts\h_wrs_responses.json
msgid ""
"Forget it, I will come for as long as I gain benefits from doing this crap! "
"Besides, I am grateful that you've came to pick me up."
msgstr ""

#: .\Modification_Files\NPC\v_npc_responds\Wastelands_Outskirts\h_wrs_responses.json
msgid "Lets go!"
msgstr ""

#: .\Modification_Files\NPC\v_npc_responds\Wastelands_Outskirts\v_vgs_responses.json
msgid "Mortal! Struggling to live?"
msgstr ""

#: .\Modification_Files\NPC\v_npc_responds\Wastelands_Outskirts\v_vgs_responses.json
msgid "Yes, and true."
msgstr ""

#: .\Modification_Files\NPC\v_npc_responds\Wastelands_Outskirts\v_vgs_responses.json
msgid "Now, you want something from me?"
msgstr ""

#: .\Modification_Files\NPC\v_npc_responds\Wastelands_Outskirts\v_vgs_responses.json
msgid "Where did these guns came from?"
msgstr ""

#: .\Modification_Files\NPC\v_npc_responds\Wastelands_Outskirts\v_vgs_responses.json
msgid "I want to buy."
msgstr ""

#: .\Modification_Files\NPC\v_npc_responds\Wastelands_Outskirts\v_vgs_responses.json
msgid "Maybe later."
msgstr ""

#: .\Modification_Files\NPC\v_npc_responds\Wastelands_Outskirts\v_vgs_responses.json
msgid ""
"I am the gun trader here... If you're not interested with my trades, just go"
" outside."
msgstr ""

#: .\Modification_Files\NPC\v_npc_responds\Wastelands_Outskirts\v_vgs_responses.json
msgid "Thanks for your info."
msgstr ""

#: .\Modification_Files\NPC\v_npc_responds\Wastelands_Outskirts\v_vgs_responses.json
msgid ""
"These are reserved from decades 'till now. Since there's no gunsmith on our "
"side, we only got few of them."
msgstr ""

#: .\Modification_Files\NPC\v_npc_responds\Wastelands_Outskirts\v_vgs_responses.json
msgid "Can I get something from you for free?"
msgstr ""

#: .\Modification_Files\NPC\v_npc_responds\Wastelands_Outskirts\v_vgs_responses.json
msgid "Sound hard-to-get."
msgstr ""

#: .\Modification_Files\NPC\v_npc_responds\Wastelands_Outskirts\v_vgs_responses.json
msgid "I see that you've met my commander... What do you want?"
msgstr ""

#: .\Modification_Files\NPC\v_npc_responds\Wastelands_Outskirts\v_vgs_responses.json
msgid "Ofcourse not! You want it, then buy it."
msgstr ""

#: .\Modification_Files\NPC\v_npc_responds\Wastelands_Outskirts\v_vgs_responses.json
msgid "Well, okay..."
msgstr ""

#: .\Modification_Files\NPC\v_npc_responds\Wastelands_Outskirts\v_vgs_responses.json
msgid "The commando told me about the supplies..."
msgstr ""

#: .\Modification_Files\NPC\v_npc_responds\Wastelands_Outskirts\v_vgs_responses.json
msgid ""
"The supplies that were stocked in here are some spare draw kits, a bag and "
"blood powders. Will you take them?"
msgstr ""

#: .\Modification_Files\NPC\v_npc_responds\Wastelands_Outskirts\v_vgs_responses.json
msgid "But he told me to get some guns from you?"
msgstr ""

#: .\Modification_Files\NPC\v_npc_responds\Wastelands_Outskirts\v_vgs_responses.json
msgid "Okay, I'll take them!"
msgstr ""

#: .\Modification_Files\NPC\v_npc_responds\Wastelands_Outskirts\v_vgs_responses.json
msgid ""
"Umm... I could give you the oldest prototype of vampiric guns I got here:\n"
"The blood slinger."
msgstr ""

#: .\Modification_Files\NPC\v_npc_responds\Wastelands_Outskirts\v_vgs_responses.json
msgid "Seems legit. I'll take it!"
msgstr ""

#: .\Modification_Files\NPC\v_npc_responds\Wastelands_Outskirts\v_vgs_responses.json
msgid ""
"I guess not... Its like a garbaged project you vampires been doing for these"
" days."
msgstr ""

#: .\Modification_Files\NPC\v_npc_responds\Wastelands_Outskirts\v_vgs_responses.json
msgid "I guess not..."
msgstr ""

#: .\Modification_Files\NPC\v_npc_responds\Wastelands_Outskirts\v_vgs_responses.json
msgid "Tell him that we don't have any spare guns to give."
msgstr ""

#: .\Modification_Files\NPC\v_npc_responds\Wastelands_Outskirts\v_wg1_responses.json
msgid "You've come a long way, mortal."
msgstr ""

#: .\Modification_Files\NPC\v_npc_responds\Wastelands_Outskirts\v_wg1_responses.json
msgid "I know."
msgstr ""

#: .\Modification_Files\NPC\v_npc_responds\Wastelands_Outskirts\v_wg1_responses.json
msgid "Yes, I know."
msgstr ""

#: .\Modification_Files\NPC\v_npc_responds\Wastelands_Outskirts\v_wg1_responses.json
msgid "I want to talk about something..."
msgstr ""

#: .\Modification_Files\NPC\v_npc_responds\Wastelands_Outskirts\v_wg1_responses.json
msgid "Talk about what?"
msgstr ""

#: .\Modification_Files\NPC\v_npc_responds\Wastelands_Outskirts\v_wg1_responses.json
msgid "You should be safe here, so don't do anything stupid."
msgstr ""

#: .\Modification_Files\NPC\v_npc_responds\Wastelands_Outskirts\v_wg1_responses.json
msgid "Where am I?."
msgstr ""

#: .\Modification_Files\NPC\v_npc_responds\Wastelands_Outskirts\v_wg1_responses.json
msgid "The commando has sent me to this place."
msgstr ""

#: .\Modification_Files\NPC\v_npc_responds\Wastelands_Outskirts\v_wg1_responses.json
msgid "You know a place like this?"
msgstr ""

#: .\Modification_Files\NPC\v_npc_responds\Wastelands_Outskirts\v_wg1_responses.json
msgid "You need a volunteer for jobs?"
msgstr ""

#: .\Modification_Files\NPC\v_npc_responds\Wastelands_Outskirts\v_wg1_responses.json
#: .\Modification_Files\NPC\v_npc_responds\Wastelands_Outskirts\v_wg2_responses.json
msgid "Okay. Bye."
msgstr ""

#: .\Modification_Files\NPC\v_npc_responds\Wastelands_Outskirts\v_wg1_responses.json
msgid "Nevermind. I'll be going now..."
msgstr ""

#: .\Modification_Files\NPC\v_npc_responds\Wastelands_Outskirts\v_wg1_responses.json
msgid ""
"You're in the sanctuary for both humans and vampires, the wasteland "
"outskirts. Here, we protect each other from savage entities and serves as an"
" outpost for those luckily survived ones."
msgstr ""

#: .\Modification_Files\NPC\v_npc_responds\Wastelands_Outskirts\v_wg1_responses.json
msgid "Okay, thanks for the info."
msgstr ""

#: .\Modification_Files\NPC\v_npc_responds\Wastelands_Outskirts\v_wg1_responses.json
msgid ""
"Hmm, so they have sent you here... For what reason? Everything's fine as it "
"is."
msgstr ""

#: .\Modification_Files\NPC\v_npc_responds\Wastelands_Outskirts\v_wg1_responses.json
msgid "So... Will you tell me where it is?"
msgstr ""

#: .\Modification_Files\NPC\v_npc_responds\Wastelands_Outskirts\v_wg1_responses.json
msgid "Oh, okay... Is there something I could help you with?"
msgstr ""

#: .\Modification_Files\NPC\v_npc_responds\Wastelands_Outskirts\v_wg1_responses.json
msgid "No."
msgstr ""

#: .\Modification_Files\NPC\v_npc_responds\Wastelands_Outskirts\v_wg1_responses.json
msgid ""
"If you're willing to help us, ask the other guard by the entrance. He might "
"need your assistance in dealing with labor and stuff."
msgstr ""

#: .\Modification_Files\NPC\v_npc_responds\Wastelands_Outskirts\v_wg1_responses.json
msgid "See ya then!"
msgstr ""

#: .\Modification_Files\NPC\v_npc_responds\Wastelands_Outskirts\v_wg1_responses.json
msgid "I'm just a guard, I have no problems with my position."
msgstr ""

#: .\Modification_Files\NPC\v_npc_responds\Wastelands_Outskirts\v_wg1_responses.json
msgid "The commando has sent me here."
msgstr ""

#: .\Modification_Files\NPC\v_npc_responds\Wastelands_Outskirts\v_wg2_responses.json
msgid "What do you seek?"
msgstr ""

#: .\Modification_Files\NPC\v_npc_responds\Wastelands_Outskirts\v_wg2_responses.json
msgid "What do you want?"
msgstr ""

#: .\Modification_Files\NPC\v_npc_responds\Wastelands_Outskirts\v_wg2_responses.json
msgid "What are you looking for?"
msgstr ""

#: .\Modification_Files\NPC\v_npc_responds\Wastelands_Outskirts\v_wg2_responses.json
msgid "Just come in..."
msgstr ""

#: .\Modification_Files\NPC\v_npc_responds\Wastelands_Outskirts\v_wg2_responses.json
msgid "Let's talk for a moment."
msgstr ""

#: .\Modification_Files\NPC\v_npc_responds\Wastelands_Outskirts\v_wg2_responses.json
msgid "I want to talk with you..."
msgstr ""

#: .\Modification_Files\NPC\v_npc_responds\Wastelands_Outskirts\v_wg2_responses.json
msgid "I guess you're important. What is it?"
msgstr ""

#: .\Modification_Files\NPC\v_npc_responds\Wastelands_Outskirts\v_wg2_responses.json
msgid "No..."
msgstr ""

#: .\Modification_Files\NPC\v_npc_responds\Wastelands_Outskirts\v_wg2_responses.json
msgid "No!"
msgstr ""

#: .\Modification_Files\NPC\v_npc_responds\Wastelands_Outskirts\v_wg2_responses.json
msgid "The guard told me you need my help."
msgstr ""

#: .\Modification_Files\NPC\v_npc_responds\Wastelands_Outskirts\v_wg2_responses.json
msgid "How's the life here?"
msgstr ""

#: .\Modification_Files\NPC\v_npc_responds\Wastelands_Outskirts\v_wg2_responses.json
msgid "About that job..."
msgstr ""

#: .\Modification_Files\NPC\v_npc_responds\Wastelands_Outskirts\v_wg2_responses.json
msgid "Something I need to do?"
msgstr ""

#: .\Modification_Files\NPC\v_npc_responds\Wastelands_Outskirts\v_wg2_responses.json
msgid "I better get going..."
msgstr ""

#: .\Modification_Files\NPC\v_npc_responds\Wastelands_Outskirts\v_wg2_responses.json
msgid "You're at the wasteland outskirts, now move, mortal."
msgstr ""

#: .\Modification_Files\NPC\v_npc_responds\Wastelands_Outskirts\v_wg2_responses.json
msgid "Wait. I want to know more about the places you know..."
msgstr ""

#: .\Modification_Files\NPC\v_npc_responds\Wastelands_Outskirts\v_wg2_responses.json
msgid "Okay, I'll move."
msgstr ""

#: .\Modification_Files\NPC\v_npc_responds\Wastelands_Outskirts\v_wg2_responses.json
msgid "Like what?"
msgstr ""

#: .\Modification_Files\NPC\v_npc_responds\Wastelands_Outskirts\v_wg2_responses.json
msgid "About HIM's location?"
msgstr ""

#: .\Modification_Files\NPC\v_npc_responds\Wastelands_Outskirts\v_wg2_responses.json
msgid "Actually, nevermind..."
msgstr ""

#: .\Modification_Files\NPC\v_npc_responds\Wastelands_Outskirts\v_wg2_responses.json
msgid ""
"I know you've been told its a deep secret, but why do you mind about our "
"master?"
msgstr ""

#: .\Modification_Files\NPC\v_npc_responds\Wastelands_Outskirts\v_wg2_responses.json
msgid "I'd like to meet HIM."
msgstr ""

#: .\Modification_Files\NPC\v_npc_responds\Wastelands_Outskirts\v_wg2_responses.json
msgid "HE looks questionable."
msgstr ""

#: .\Modification_Files\NPC\v_npc_responds\Wastelands_Outskirts\v_wg2_responses.json
msgid "I want to know HIS upcoming actions."
msgstr ""

#: .\Modification_Files\NPC\v_npc_responds\Wastelands_Outskirts\v_wg2_responses.json
msgid "Forget it..."
msgstr ""

#: .\Modification_Files\NPC\v_npc_responds\Wastelands_Outskirts\v_wg2_responses.json
msgid "In which will never happen to a human."
msgstr ""

#: .\Modification_Files\NPC\v_npc_responds\Wastelands_Outskirts\v_wg2_responses.json
msgid "I guess I've talked about everything..."
msgstr ""

#: .\Modification_Files\NPC\v_npc_responds\Wastelands_Outskirts\v_wg2_responses.json
msgid " That sucks..."
msgstr ""

#: .\Modification_Files\NPC\v_npc_responds\Wastelands_Outskirts\v_wg2_responses.json
msgid "I know. HE's full of mysteries even me can't talk about."
msgstr ""

#: .\Modification_Files\NPC\v_npc_responds\Wastelands_Outskirts\v_wg2_responses.json
msgid "Trust me, human, HIS movements are for the good cause."
msgstr ""

#: .\Modification_Files\NPC\v_npc_responds\Wastelands_Outskirts\v_wg2_responses.json
msgid "Oh, okay then..."
msgstr ""

#: .\Modification_Files\NPC\v_npc_responds\Wastelands_Outskirts\v_wg2_responses.json
msgid ""
"Don't worry, mortal. Eventually, you'll meet someone to quench your thirst "
"for deeper answers."
msgstr ""

#: .\Modification_Files\NPC\v_npc_responds\Wastelands_Outskirts\v_wg2_responses.json
msgid "Uhh, okay..."
msgstr ""

#: .\Modification_Files\NPC\v_npc_responds\Wastelands_Outskirts\v_wg2_responses.json
msgid "Uhh, okay... I'll expect that."
msgstr ""

#: .\Modification_Files\NPC\v_npc_responds\Wastelands_Outskirts\v_wg2_responses.json
msgid ""
"Nah, I'm just a guard here doing my job. If you want to know more, seek the "
"guard in the kitchen."
msgstr ""

#: .\Modification_Files\NPC\v_npc_responds\Wastelands_Outskirts\v_wg2_responses.json
msgid "He told me to help you with something."
msgstr ""

#: .\Modification_Files\NPC\v_npc_responds\Wastelands_Outskirts\v_wg2_responses.json
msgid "Okay, I'm going..."
msgstr ""

#: .\Modification_Files\NPC\v_npc_responds\Wastelands_Outskirts\v_wg2_responses.json
msgid ""
"So you're interested in helping us out with our problems... But I don't want"
" to get you in trouble."
msgstr ""

#: .\Modification_Files\NPC\v_npc_responds\Wastelands_Outskirts\v_wg2_responses.json
msgid "I'll take the risk!"
msgstr ""

#: .\Modification_Files\NPC\v_npc_responds\Wastelands_Outskirts\v_wg2_responses.json
msgid "Forget it, I'm out of that!"
msgstr ""

#: .\Modification_Files\NPC\v_npc_responds\Wastelands_Outskirts\v_wg2_responses.json
msgid "If you insist..."
msgstr ""

#: .\Modification_Files\NPC\v_npc_responds\Wastelands_Outskirts\v_wg2_responses.json
msgid ""
"We've got some cows here as our food source and a water nearby for humans to"
" quench their thirst."
msgstr ""

#: .\Modification_Files\NPC\v_npc_responds\Wastelands_Outskirts\v_wg2_responses.json
msgid "I mean what are you vampires drinking?"
msgstr ""

#: .\Modification_Files\NPC\v_npc_responds\Wastelands_Outskirts\v_wg2_responses.json
msgid "Cows? Where'd you get them?"
msgstr ""

#: .\Modification_Files\NPC\v_npc_responds\Wastelands_Outskirts\v_wg2_responses.json
msgid ""
"Blood, ofcourse! We drink blood from the cows as our substitute to human's. "
"Don't worry about the refugees here, we tend to protect them as ordered."
msgstr ""

#: .\Modification_Files\NPC\v_npc_responds\Wastelands_Outskirts\v_wg2_responses.json
msgid ""
"We herd them from the wilderness. We don't know if they came from the "
"nearest farm, but certainly they are free from infection."
msgstr ""

